NK010(tha)032:2: chos dbyings ngang las bskyod pa med pa'i ngang //
NK010(tha)032:3: phrin las mi g.yo gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul //
NK010(tha)032:4: drag shul rngam pa'i las la thogs pa med //
NK010(tha)032:5: sgrol ba'i yum mchog e ka dz+aa ti ma //
NK010(tha)032:6: phrin las rnam bzhis dgra bgegs 'dul mdzad cing //
NK010(tha)032:7: ye shes phur pas thams cad dbyings su 'debs //
NK010(tha)032:8: dug lnga'i bdud 'dul khro mchog 'dus pa'i sku'i //
NK010(tha)032:9: rigs lnga'i sras mchog badz+ra k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)032:10: dbus phyogs gtso bo yab yum sras mchog bcas /
NK010(tha)032:12: rol pa'i stobs kyis gza' skar tshar gcod cing //
NK010(tha)032:13: 'dod chags skyon spangs sku yi dbang phyug che //
NK010(tha)032:14: ye shes mthar phyin nyi zla'i 'od bzhin gsal //
NK010(tha)032:15: skye bzhi mos pas skye la /
NK010(tha)032:17: mtshan ma med pa'i dbyings thos rig pa'i sgra //
NK010(tha)032:18: dbyings nyid rig shes dbyings la snyan nyan kyang /
NK010(tha)032:20: de la bstan pa gsung gi sgra 'byin pa //
NK010(tha)032:21: khams gsum h'u mdzad mnyes byed sgra bya mi ta /
NK010(tha)032:24: gzhan na sgra 'byin rlung 'byin ma bsnol 'dug dpyad /
NK010(tha)032:25: khro bcu'i bstod pa myang 'das na /
NK010(tha)032:26: rlung 'byin sgra 'byin gnyis min tshad gcig tu 'dus so //
NK010(tha)032:27: lhag mthong chos dbyings zhi gnas rlan gyis brgyal //
NK010(tha)032:28: 'khor ba thugs rje'i smon lam stobs kyis myos //
NK010(tha)032:29: rtog 'joms rdzas la gtsang dme med par rol //
NK010(tha)032:30: de phyir phra men myos byed phag gi dbu //
NK010(tha)032:31: 'jug pa rang dbang med pa'i gnyid gyur pa //
NK010(tha)032:32: mnyam pa'i chos rtogs log lta myos byed cing //
NK010(tha)032:33: 'khor ba'i nyon mongs thams cad myos par byed //
NK010(tha)032:34: thams cad myos byed phra men smrig bu'i dbu //
NK010(tha)032:35: steng phyogs khro bo yab yum phra men bcas /
NK010(tha)032:37: bzlog pa'i stobs kyis lha rnams tshar gcod cing //
NK010(tha)032:38: ma byin len pa'i skyon spangs dbang phyug che //
NK010(tha)032:39: rab tu shes pa'i shes rab mthar phyin pa //
NK010(tha)032:41: byad dbang mdzad khro bo rnam par rgyal //
NK010(tha)032:42: ye shes thugs rje zin pas mthar mi 'chang //
NK010(tha)032:43: thugs rje ye shes zin pas srid las grol //
NK010(tha)032:44: gnyis la mi gnas mtha' bral dbu mar snyems //
NK010(tha)032:45: rnam par rgyal ba mnyes mdzad rab snyems ma //
NK010(tha)032:46: sdug bsngal thugs rje mi bzod phrin las dpa' //
NK010(tha)032:47: yal bar mi 'dor brtson 'grus shugs kyis brtul //
NK010(tha)032:48: gdod nas dag pas 'khor ba mthar thug sgrol //
NK010(tha)032:49: de phyir dpal rtul za byed stag gi dbu //
NK010(tha)032:50: yid g.yo las can sems par gyur pa ni //
NK010(tha)032:51: ye shes dbang gis thugs rje 'gro la g.yo //
NK010(tha)032:52: don mdzad god 'phrang ye shes dbyings su mkhyen //
NK010(tha)032:53: de phyir tshul khrims chen mo bya rgod dbu //
NK010(tha)032:54: shar gyi khro bo yab yum phra men bcas //
NK010(tha)032:56: 'dzin tshul stobs kyis drang srong tshar gcod cing //
NK010(tha)032:57: log lta'i skyon spangs yang dag lta dang ldan //
NK010(tha)032:58: tshul khrims mthar phyin drang srong spyod pas che //
NK010(tha)032:59: ye shes dbang mdzad khro chen dbyug sngon can //
NK010(tha)032:60: rig pa'i sder chen chos kyi dbyings nyid 'dzin //
NK010(tha)032:61: thugs rje'i lcags kyus 'khor ba mi gtong zhing //
NK010(tha)032:62: shes rab thabs kyi lcags kyus mtha' gnyis 'dzin //
NK010(tha)032:63: dbyug pa sngon po mnyes mdzad rdo rje sder //
NK010(tha)032:64: sdang mig thugs rje mi 'gyur zhe la gnon //
NK010(tha)032:65: mthu rtsal rngam brjid 'gyur med bdud dpung bzlog /
NK010(tha)032:66: tsham rngams ral bsigs gdang ngar 'jig rten 'gengs //
NK010(tha)032:67: de phyir phra men 'gyur med g.yag gi dbu //
NK010(tha)032:68: bsam pa'i dngos po 'dod la 'dun par gyur //
NK010(tha)032:69: dbyings nyid ye shes mkhyen pas shes bya za //
NK010(tha)032:70: thugs rje 'dun pas 'khor ba'i bag chags sbyangs //
NK010(tha)032:71: de phyir phra men za byed bya rog dbu //
NK010(tha)032:72: shar lho'i khro bo yab yum phra men bcas //
NK010(tha)032:74: 'jigs byed stobs kyis 'chi bdag zil gnon cing //
NK010(tha)032:75: srog gcod nyes spangs sku yi dbang phyug che //
NK010(tha)032:76: gzung 'dzin skyon spangs bsam gtan ngang la gnas //
NK010(tha)032:77: tshe la dbang mdzad 'jigs byed gshin rje gshed //
NK010(tha)032:78: ye shes mtshan sdud thugs rje'i dur khrod 'byung //
NK010(tha)032:79: sprul pas 'gro bsgral sku dang ye shes 'phro //
NK010(tha)032:80: shes snying ma skyes dbu ma'i rig pa skyed //
NK010(tha)032:81: khro rgyal gshin rje mnyes mdzad dur khrod bdag /
NK010(tha)032:83: dgra spangs dran pa'i dgon par gnas //
NK010(tha)032:84: 'khrul skyon dri ma shes bzhin rdzis tshor spong //
NK010(tha)032:85: 'gro don dus la bab na thugs rje 'jug /
NK010(tha)032:86: de phyir phra men 'jug byed sha ba'i dbu //
NK010(tha)032:87: dmigs la sems 'dzin yid la byed par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)032:88: ye shes dbyings su rtog drangs nyin mo nyal //
NK010(tha)032:89: 'gro mdongs rmongs la thugs rjes mtshan mo ldangs //
NK010(tha)032:90: ye shes thugs rjes drangs pa 'ug pa'i dbu //
NK010(tha)032:91: lho yi khro bo yab yum phra men bcas //
NK010(tha)032:93: brdeg pa'i stobs kyis srin po tshar gcod cing //
NK010(tha)032:94: rdzun gyi skyon spangs ngag gi dbang phyug che //
NK010(tha)032:95: thabs kyi stobs kyis mtshan ma 'dul mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)032:97: la dbang mdzad bran tshul mig g.yo mgon //
NK010(tha)032:98: dbyings su mtshan ma shes rab tho bas brdungs //
NK010(tha)032:99: thugs rje'i phrin las sems can mtshan ma 'joms //
NK010(tha)032:100: dbu mar ye shes snying rjes mi rtog ngang //
NK010(tha)032:101: mi g.yo mgon po mnyes mdzad gtun khung ma //
NK010(tha)032:102: chos dbyings gnas la rtog pa'i skyon sel zhing //
NK010(tha)032:103: thugs rje'i sprul pa'i spu ris bsam mi khyab //
NK010(tha)032:104: dug gsum mi spong sha khrag rus la rol //
NK010(tha)032:105: sel byed sprul pas don mdzad gzig gi dbu //
NK010(tha)032:107: pa'i dngos la rtse gcig ting 'dzin gyur //
NK010(tha)032:108: mnyam nyid mtha' bral dbyings las mi g.yo bar //
NK010(tha)032:109: rtog ge'i spyod yul byis pas mi mthong sbeed //
NK010(tha)032:110: de phyir phra men sbed byed khwa yi dbu //
NK010(tha)032:111: lho nub khro bo yab yum phra men bcas //
NK010(tha)032:113: brjid pa'i stobs kyi klu rnams zil gyis gnon //
NK010(tha)032:115: skyon spong ngag gi dbang phyug che //
NK010(tha)032:116: 'bad pa med pa'i brtson 'grus shugs dang ldan //
NK010(tha)032:117: chos la dbang mdzad ha ya g+r+ai ba dpal //
NK010(tha)032:118: rdo rje gtum mos mtshan ma'i dngos po bcom //
NK010(tha)032:119: thugs rje rngams tshul srid pa thal bar brlag /
NK010(tha)032:120: gnyis la mi gnas mtha' bral dbu mar bsdigs //
NK010(tha)032:121: ha ya g+r+ai ba mnyes mdzad ral gcig ma'ang /
NK010(tha)032:123: yang bag zon chags 'gro don thabs mkhas ldan //
NK010(tha)032:124: mi 'dul zung thub btang snyoms chen por bzhugs //
NK010(tha)032:125: dus la bab na brtson 'grus shugs dang ldan //
NK010(tha)032:126: de phyir mkhas brtson mdzad pa byi la'i dbu //
NK010(tha)032:127: las 'bras bden la yid ches dad par gyur //
NK010(tha)032:128: mnyam nyid dbyings su ye shes shugs kyis mgyogs //
NK010(tha)032:129: zhi gnas spyan gyis lhag mthong bgrod tshegs chung //
NK010(tha)032:130: de phyir phra men mgyogs byed pu shud dbu //
NK010(tha)032:131: nub kyi khro bo yab yum phra men bcas //
NK010(tha)032:133: shugs 'chang stobs kyis rlung lha tshar gcod cing //
NK010(tha)032:135: ba'i skyon spang ngag gi dbang phyug che //
NK010(tha)032:136: 'dod pa kun tu sbyin mdzad rgyal po'i tshul //
NK010(tha)032:138: dbang mdzad khro bo gzhan gyi mi thub rgyal kyang /
NK010(tha)032:140: phra mor 'bigs pa ye shes dbyings su 'phen //
NK010(tha)032:141: ye shes mda' ni gnad du thugs rjes brdeg /
NK010(tha)032:142: ma 'khyogs dbu ma chen po'i don rtogs las //
NK010(tha)032:143: gzhan gyis mi thub mnyes mdzad mda' snyem ma //
NK010(tha)032:144: ye shes dbyings la 'jug pas shes bya za //
NK010(tha)032:145: dbyings nyid ye shes la 'jug nyon mongs za //
NK010(tha)032:146: gnyis med ye shes phrin las 'khor ba za //
NK010(tha)032:147: de phyir za byed chen mo spyang ki'i dbu //
NK010(tha)032:148: nges pa'i dngos por 'dzin pa'i mos par gyur //
NK010(tha)032:149: lhag mthong ye shes dbyings nyid mnyam gyur 'dzin //
NK010(tha)032:150: zhi ga nas gces par 'dzin pa mi 'jog pa //
NK010(tha)032:151: de phyir phra men 'dzin byed khra yi dbu //
NK010(tha)032:152: nub byang khro bo yab yum phra men bcas //
NK010(tha)032:155: 'tshir ba'i stobs kyis gnod sbyin zhabs kyis gnon //
NK010(tha)032:157: ngag rtsub skyon spang ngag gi dbang phyug che //
NK010(tha)032:158: smon lam mthar phyin bdud 'dul thugs rje'i rtsi //
NK010(tha)032:159: las la dbang mdzad bdud rtsi kun+da li //
NK010(tha)032:160: bskyod pa'i ye shes sa rnams dus gcig gcod //
NK010(tha)032:161: thugs rje'i shugs kyis 'gro rnams gnas nas spor //
NK010(tha)032:162: thabs dang shes rab spyod pas mtha' gnyis spor //
NK010(tha)032:163: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba mnyes mdzad rlung 'byin ma //
NK010(tha)032:164: rigs btsun gnyan por gyur pas thams cad 'dul //
NK010(tha)032:165: phrin las rtsal gyis bdud dpung ma lus 'joms //
NK010(tha)032:166: stong nyid sgra bsgrags mu stegs wa tshogs 'jigs //
NK010(tha)032:167: de phyir 'joms byed rtsal mchog seng ge'i dbu //
NK010(tha)032:168: 'dris pa'i dngos po ma brjed dran par gyur //
NK010(tha)032:169: dbyings dang ye shes mnyam nyid ma brjed dran //
NK010(tha)032:170: ting 'dzin 'bum phrag lhag mthong so sor gsal //
NK010(tha)032:171: gnyis la ma rmongs sgron ma pha wang dbu //
NK010(tha)032:172: byang gi khro bo yab yum phra men bcas //
NK010(tha)032:174: gnon pa'i stobs kyis 'byung po tshar gcod cing //
NK010(tha)032:175: gnod sems nyes spangs thugs kyi dbang phyug che //
NK010(tha)032:176: gnyan po'i stobs kyis mi mthun zil gyis gnon //
NK010(tha)032:178: 'phrul dbang mdzad khams gsum pad+ma 'khyil ba'ang dpyad /
NK010(tha)032:180: bdag rtog log lta'i mtshan ma kun bcoms nas //
NK010(tha)032:181: za byed mche bas skye shi rtsad bcad de //
NK010(tha)032:182: sku dang ye shes ma skyes mi dmigs pa //
NK010(tha)032:183: khams gsum rnam rgyal mnyes mdzad gsod byed ma //
NK010(tha)032:184: dbyings la ye shes nyal zhing thugs rje rmi //
NK010(tha)032:185: mthing nag gcer bu drag po'i skur ston cing //
NK010(tha)032:186: thugs mchog rnam dag chos nyid dbyings su mkhyen //
NK010(tha)032:187: de phyir phra men rmi byed dom gyi dbu //
NK010(tha)032:188: chos rnams 'byed pa med pa'i gnas gyur pa'i //
NK010(tha)032:189: mnyam nyid ngang du log lta sel byed cing //
NK010(tha)032:190: rig pa bskyed pas som nyi the tshom gcod //
NK010(tha)032:191: de phyir phra men gsod byed sre mo'i dbu //
NK010(tha)032:192: byang shar khro bo yab yum phra men bcas //
NK010(tha)032:195: pa'i stobs kyis sa bdag tshar gcod cing //
NK010(tha)032:196: brnab sems skyon spangs thugs kyi dbang phyug che //
NK010(tha)032:197: bzod pa sa gzhi lta bu'i go cha dgos //
NK010(tha)032:199: lam dbang mdzad 'jigs byed stobs po che //
NK010(tha)032:200: thugs dam dbang gis rnam dag dbyings nas bskul //
NK010(tha)032:201: thugs rje'i shugs kyis 'gro ba gnas nas 'dren //
NK010(tha)032:202: gnyis med mchod bskul dbu ma'i dgyes pa stob //
NK010(tha)032:203: ma h+aa ba la mnyes mdzad bskyod tsun+de dang bskul byed ma'ang zer /
NK010(tha)032:205: ye shes thugs rje'i stobs kyis mtha' gnyis gnon //
NK010(tha)032:206: tsham rngams ral bsigs sprul pas bdud dpung 'joms //
NK010(tha)032:207: las su ci mdzad brtson 'grus stobs kyis rol //
NK010(tha)032:208: de phyir phra men stobs ldan dred kyi dbu //
NK010(tha)032:209: gsum 'dus gcod pa'i reg par gyur pa ni //
NK010(tha)032:210: phrin las bye brag mang po ci mdzad kyang //
NK010(tha)032:211: phyag rgya bzhi ru ma skyes dbyings su 'bros //
NK010(tha)032:212: de phyir phra men 'bros byed byi ba'i dbu //
NK010(tha)032:213: 'og gi khro bo yab yum phra men bcas //
NK010(tha)032:215: 'khor ba rdo rje brjod pas mya ngan 'das //
NK010(tha)032:216: chos sku rdo rje brjod pas mtha' gnyis spang //
NK010(tha)032:217: rjod byed brjod bral don gyi tshig dang bral //
NK010(tha)032:218: de phyir brjod med rdo rje lcags kyu ma //
NK010(tha)032:219: chos nyid rdo rjes mtshan ma'i dngos po bshig /
NK010(tha)032:220: ye shes rdo rjes gzung 'dzin rtog pa bsregs //
NK010(tha)032:221: phyag mtshan rdo rjes dregs pa lha bdud 'joms //
NK010(tha)032:222: de phyir 'joms byed rdo rje zhags pa ma //
NK010(tha)032:223: 'chi med bdud rtsis yul sems skye 'gag med //
NK010(tha)032:224: grub pa'i bdud rtsis bsam pa'i 'bras bu thob //
NK010(tha)032:225: thugs rjes 'gro bdud rtsi gtong bla med sgrub //
NK010(tha)032:226: rtsi mchog ye shes rdo rje lcags sgrog ma //
NK010(tha)032:227: ye shes 'khrol byed yon tan rgya mtsho sgrub //
NK010(tha)032:228: thugs rje 'khrol byed 'jig rten dbang du sdud //
NK010(tha)032:229: ye shes thugs rjes gnyis med dbyings su 'dus //
NK010(tha)032:230: de phyir brlag byed rdo rje dril 'khrol ma //
NK010(tha)032:231: ye shes sgo ma chen mo bzhi rnams kyis //
NK010(tha)032:233: phur pa lha rgyud kyi rtog pa 'di rgyud lung
NK010(tha)032:234: man ngag gi yig cha rnams go bsdur te gab
NK010(tha)032:235: dkrugs rnams go rim bsdebs shing /
NK010(tha)032:236: 'gyur khyad rnams don gang legs bzung /
NK010(tha)032:237: yig skyon rnams dag par byas te /
NK010(tha)032:238: mi pham 'jam dpal rdo rjes sgrub khang bdud las
NK010(tha)032:239: rnam rgyal gling du dga' ba chu 'brug lo'i sprel
NK010(tha)032:240: zla'i yar tshes gsum pa la yi ger dag par
NK010(tha)032:243: dgra bgegs sha khrag mchod pa 'di bzhes nas //
NK010(tha)032:244: rnal 'byor bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa la //
NK010(tha)032:245: pha rol mi dang mi min bsam ngan gyi //
NK010(tha)032:246: rig sngags rbod gtong mthu gtad ngan sbyor sogs //
NK010(tha)032:247: mi mthun 'gal rkyen gnod pa'i phyogs rnams kun //
NK010(tha)032:248: bzlog cing bsgyur ba'i phrin las dus la bab //
NK010(tha)032:249: dam nyams byad ma rang gshed rang la phob //
NK010(tha)032:250: dgra bgegs byad ma sod cig m+aa ra ya zhes sbyar /
NK010(tha)032:252: shwa na bdag nyid sa bdag chen mo bzhi //
NK010(tha)032:253: bse lcags dung gi skyes bu ging chen gsum //
NK010(tha)032:254: dkar bdud lcam dral 'byung po ser po sogs //
NK010(tha)032:255: dpal chen rdo rje phur pa'i srung ma rnams //
NK010(tha)032:256: dgra bgegs sha khrag mchod pa sogs sbyar ro //
NK010(tha)032:258: dgongs su gsol lo rig 'dzin rtsa ba gsum //
NK010(tha)032:259: gzigs su gsol lo bstan srung dam can tshogs //
NK010(tha)032:260: mkhyen par gsol lo snang srid dregs pa'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)032:261: sgrib med spyan gyis legs nyes shan phyes shig /
NK010(tha)032:262: bsam sbyor mda' bzhin bsrangs pa'i rnal 'byor la //
NK010(tha)032:263: bslu sems gzhu bzhin 'khyogs pa skye bo'i sems //
NK010(tha)032:264: rang byas med pa'i gzhan byas ngan pa la //
NK010(tha)032:265: rting gcod khyed rang rnams las gzhan su zhig /
NK010(tha)032:266: gal te rang nyid bsam sbyor ma drang na //
NK010(tha)032:267: mkhyen ldan rnams kyis bdag la ci zhig bgyi //
NK010(tha)032:268: rang nyid drang bzhin gzhan gyis 'tshe ba na //
NK010(tha)032:269: drang mkhan gnyan po med dam ga nyid la song //
NK010(tha)032:270: srid pa'i mkha' la legs nyes 'byed pa'i spyan //
NK010(tha)032:271: nyi zla ltar 'bar nam yang mi bslu ba //
NK010(tha)032:272: snang zhing srid pa'i drang mkhan mthu bo che //
NK010(tha)032:273: khyod kyis mi mthong pa ni yongs med cing //
NK010(tha)032:274: tshul ldan rnams la dgyes pa'i spyan ras ngom //
NK010(tha)032:275: tshul min rnams la sdang mig drug char 'beb //
NK010(tha)032:276: de ring gzu dang dpang po khyod la bcol //
NK010(tha)032:277: khyod min rnal 'byor rnams la dpang po med //
NK010(tha)032:278: snang srid gsal ba'i spyan gyis da ltos la //
NK010(tha)032:279: drang shan 'byed pa'i gnam thig drang por thobs //
NK010(tha)032:280: legs nyes rting gcod 'bar ba'i ral gri gdengs //
NK010(tha)032:281: phrin las dus la babs po sa ma ya //
